Van Rompuy Says Economic Situation Deteriorating, Growth Slowing

-- B y   A n d r e w   C l a p h a m
-- 
2011-10-20T11:55:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-20/van-rompuy-says-economic-situation-deteriorating-growth-slowing.html
The economic situation is
deteriorating with growth slowing in  Europe  and globally,
notably because of risks linked to the sovereign debt crisis in
some countries, European Union President Herman van Rompuy said
in a letter to European leaders.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
